headline: Chartis Names FICO an Enterprise Fraud Solutions Category Leader for Fifth Straight Report
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., August 27, 2025--Global analytics software leader FICO today announced that it has been named a category leader for enterprise fraud solutions for the fifth time in a row in Chartis’ Enterprise and Payment Fraud Solutions 2025, Quadrant Update. FICO was listed as a category leader in three categories: enterprise fraud solutions, payment fraud solutions and fraud platforms.
